Package: simtimer
Type: Package
Title: Datetimes as Integers for Simulations
Version: 3.0.2
Date: 2017-12-19
Author: Adrian Staempfli, Christoph Strauss, Michael Schmid
Maintainer: Adrian Staempfli <adrian.staempfli@fhsg.ch>
Description: Handles datetimes as integers (called sim_datetimes) for
        the usage inside simulations. The conversion is made using the
        internally S4 generic function "as.numeric()" of the package
        base. Averill M. Law / W. David Kelton (1999,
        ISBN:0-07-059292-6) Department of Statistics, University of
        California, Berkeley (2006)
        <https://www.stat.berkeley.edu/~s133/dates.html> Department of
        Mathematics ETH ZC<rich, Switzerland (2017)
        <https://stat.ethz.ch/R-manual/R-devel/library/base/html/difftime.html>
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests: testthat, knitr, rmarkdown, microbenchmark, lubridate
URL: http://github.com/ims-fhs/simtimer
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
